        {
            "title": "亞冬會︱習近平7日晚出席開幕式  並舉行外事活動",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"亞冬會7日晚舉行開幕式，習近平將會出席，並宣布本屆亞冬會開幕。新華社\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/c645e91bb96ae56abb2479cba7e4fc0f/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250206/_2025020612324669066.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">亞冬會7日晚舉行開幕式，習近平將會出席，並宣布本屆亞冬會開幕。新華社</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>第九屆亞洲冬季運動會開幕式2月7日晚在黑龍江哈爾濱市舉行。國家主席習近平將出席開幕式並宣布本屆亞冬會開幕。\n\n</p>\n<p>7日中午，習近平主席將為來華出席開幕式的外國領導人舉行歡迎宴會。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"第九屆亞冬會明日開幕。新華社\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/5c234e1b941726d4eec4034cb17040ab/2025-02/XxjpseC007081_20250120_PEPFN0A001.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        第九屆亞冬會明日開幕。新華社\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"第九屆亞冬會明日開幕。新華社\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/28512c75562126c95efd614b1fc1e1b0/2025-02/XxjpseC007083_20250120_PEPFN0A001.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        第九屆亞冬會明日開幕。新華社\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"第九屆亞冬會明日開幕。新華社\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/1f57d0385b5701ea9aea8eba94268482/2025-02/XxjpseC007314_20250108_PEPFN0A001.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        第九屆亞冬會明日開幕。新華社\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"亞冬會7日晚舉行開幕式，習近平將會出席，並宣布本屆亞冬會開幕。新華社\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/b5b7ba2dc5c6c5aca195c1c6eceec6c8/2025-02/New_Project_XI_456546156.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        亞冬會7日晚舉行開幕式，習近平將會出席，並宣布本屆亞冬會開幕。新華社\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p>\n<p>相關新聞：<a href=\"https://www.stheadline.com/realtime-china/3425551/%E8%B0%B7%E6%84%9B%E5%87%8C%E5%AE%A3%E4%BD%88-%E5%9B%A0%E5%82%B7%E9%80%80%E5%87%BA%E5%93%88%E7%88%BE%E6%BF%B1%E4%BA%9E%E5%86%AC%E6%9C%83\">谷愛凌宣佈 因傷退出哈爾濱亞冬會</a>\n</p>\n<p>出席開幕式的外國領導人有：汶萊蘇丹哈桑納爾、吉爾吉斯斯坦總統扎帕羅夫、巴基斯坦總統扎爾達裏、泰國總理佩通坦、韓國國會議長禹元植等。\n\n</p>\n<p> \n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
